<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
    <title>Job Board</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/job.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Alumni Job Board</h1>
        <p>Explore job postings and career opportunities posted by alumni and industry partners. Find your next career move here!</p>
    </header>

    <section class="job-board-section">
        <h2>Current Job Listings</h2>
        <div class="job-listings">
            <!-- Example Job Post -->
            <div class="job-card">
                <h3>Software Engineer</h3>
                <p><strong>Company:</strong> Tech Innovators</p>
                <p><strong>Location:</strong> San Francisco, CA</p>
                <p><strong>Posted By:</strong> John Doe, Class of 2015</p>
                <p><strong>Job Description:</strong> Develop and maintain software applications in a fast-paced, agile environment.</p>
                <button class="apply-btn">Apply Now</button>
            </div>
            <!-- Add more job cards dynamically here -->
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="networking-section">
        <h2>Building a Supportive Network</h2>
        <p>
            Develop a robust network for lifelong connections and collaborative opportunities, creating an ecosystem where alumni and students can learn from and support each other. 
            Whether you're looking for advice, mentorship, or collaborative opportunities, this platform provides a space for meaningful connections.
        </p>
        <div class="networking-tips">
            <h3>Networking Tips:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Reach out to alumni in your field for career advice.</li>
                <li>Attend alumni events and virtual meetups to expand your professional network.</li>
                <li>Join industry-specific alumni groups on social media platforms.</li>
                <li>Offer your expertise to current students or recent graduates.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Alumni Network | Empowering Careers</p>
    </footer>

    <script src="/job.ejs"></script>
</body>
</html>
